      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NYOTA (1) has a strong winning strike-rate here with three wins and a placing from eight tries. Scored by 4 lengths last time (27.48) in a Novice race over 488m at this track. Looks a leading chance on best. THIS BAD BOY (2) scored two back then was always well back and could manage only a 91 length 7th at Northam (36.20). The form from his last run is stacking up nicely. Should be about the mark. YUNDERUP POCKETS (8) has some solid form under her belt and proved too classy last time to win by a nose at this track in a handy 27.88 beating Just A Duke. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Expected to feature again. DEAR ELIZA (5) is among the chances again if she runs up to the latest effort.",
